title: "US39 — Personalised reminders + alerts"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>NotificationsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>UpdateNotificationPrefs + rule controls
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>PlannedWorkout · Profile (prefs)
  A->>B: enable personalised reminders
  B->>C: setEnabled(...)
  C->>E: read active plan - workout times, rest days
  E-->>C: schedule inputs
  C-->>B: scheduled
  B-->>A: reminders tuned to the plan
  note over E: delivered via NotificationGateway (rule-based)
